**WORKAROUND**: delete contents from the IDEA cache directories manually. Sometimes it can help when simple invalidation doesn't work.
Caches location (from [here](https://www.jetbrains.com/help/idea/tuning-the-ide.html#logs-directory)):
```
~/Library/Caches/JetBrains/<product><version> on macOS
~/.cache/JetBrains/<product><version> on Linux
%LOCALAPPDATA%\JetBrains\<product><version> on Windows
```

Possible other symptoms in a `build.gradle.kts` file:
```
MISSING_DEPENDENCY_CLASS Cannot access 'org.jetbrains.kotlin.gradle.dsl.KotlinCompile' which is a supertype of 'org.jetbrains.kotlin.gradle.tasks.KotlinCompile'. Check your module classpath for missing or conflicting dependencies

Cannot access class com.android.build.gradle.api.AndroidSourceFile

Cannot access class org.jetbrains.kotlin.gradle.dsl.KotlinJvmOptions
```